title: Barcelona victorious vs. Almeria in Pique’s final game at Camp Nou | LaLiga Highlights | ESPN FC

media:group.media:title: Barcelona victorious vs. Almeria in Pique’s final game at Camp Nou | LaLiga Highlights | ESPN FC
media:group.media:description:
In Gerard Pique’s final game at Camp Nou, Barcelona gets two goals in the second half from Ousmane Dembele and Frenkie de Jong to defeat Almeria.
